@page "/projects"

<PageTitle>Projects — Sébastien Bart</PageTitle>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>My Projects</h1>
        <p>A curated selection of personal and professional work.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURED PROJECT -->
<div class="section-full">
    <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="title-accent">★</span> Featured Project</h2>
        <div class="project-card" style="border-color: var(--shadow);">
            <div class="project-card-header card-yellow">
                <h3 class="card-title" style="font-size: 2rem;">1v1 me bro</h3>
                <p class="card-meta">2020 &mdash; Video game</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card-body" style="background-color: var(--off-white);">
                <img src="images/1v1_me_bro.jpeg" alt="1v1 me bro photo" height="256px" style="margin: auto; display: block; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                <p>
                    My personal favorite, my game, is 100% handmade and homemade! 
                    From gameplay to sound, including the UIs and, of course, the programming. 
                    It's my first major personal project, and it was a real challenge I set for myself during the COVID-19 lockdown. 
                    I finally had access to good hardware capable of running Unity, and also plenty of time, so I put all of that to good use for this project.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
                    It allowed me to improve my development skills and also to understand the software development lifecycle. 
                    Although I worked alone, I got a taste of defining the specifications, designing, deploying, and maintaining the game!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card-footer" style="background-color: var(--sage); justify-content: space-between;">
                <div class="tags" style="margin: 0;">
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">Unity</span>
                    <span class="tag">C#</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-teal">Trello</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-orange">Software management</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Play Store page</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ALL PROJECTS GRID -->
<div class="section-full section-alt">
    <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="title-accent">—</span> All Projects</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">

            <!-- Project 1 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header card-teal">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Dofus - combat system</h3>
                    <p class="card-meta">2024/2025 &mdash; Fullstack</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        I was responsible for refactoring many combat preview mechanics. 
                        Far more than just simple calculations, troubleshooting bugs required me to work on the data, the client, and the server.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-footer">
                    <div class="tags" style="margin: 0; flex: 1;">
                        <span class="tag tag-blue">C#</span>
                        <span class="tag">SQL / ORACLE</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-teal">Java</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project 2 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header card-orange">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Dofus - new UIs</h3>
                    <p class="card-meta">2023 &mdash; Frontend</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        I developed the technical aspects of the game's new interfaces, taking into account the new specifications and features.
                        Working directly with the UI/UX lead, I handled everything from prototyping mockups to user testing.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-footer">
                    <div class="tags" style="margin: 0; flex: 1;">
                        <span class="tag tag-blue">C#</span>
                        <span class="tag">HTML</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-teal">CSS</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-orange">Unity</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-red">Figma</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project 3 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header card-red">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Decathlon - monitoring</h3>
                    <p class="card-meta">2020/2021 - data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        I designed and implemented KPIs and monitoring dashboards for the Decathlon production platform, with a strong focus on performance and reliability metrics.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-footer">
                    <div class="tags" style="margin: 0; flex: 1;">
                        <span class="tag tag-blue">Splunk</span>
                        <span class="tag">SQL / PostgreSQL</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-teal">SRE</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project 4 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header card-navy">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Picross Maker</h3>
                    <p class="card-meta">2021 &mdash; product owner</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        As part of learning agile methodology, I took on the role of product owner on a project 
                        I led with my fellow students. I defined the application's requirements, task priorities, 
                        and user stories.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-footer">
                    <div class="tags" style="margin: 0; flex: 1;">
                        <span class="tag tag-blue">C#</span>
                        <span class="tag">Unity</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-teal">Agile management</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project 5 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header" style="background-color: var(--mid-blue);">
                    <h3 class="card-title" style="color: var(--off-white);">Magic card finder</h3>
                    <p class="card-meta" style="color: var(--light-blue);">2021 &mdash; Solo dev</p>
