                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Started as a student project, I finalized the application and then released it on the Play Store.
                        It allows Magic: The Gathering card game players to search for cards using several specific filters 
                        and save them for easier retrieval and to monitor their price fluctuations.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card-footer">
                    <div class="tags" style="margin: 0; flex: 1;">
                        <span class="tag tag-blue">Java</span>
                        <span class="tag">Android studio</span>
                        <span class="tag tag-teal">API rest</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project 6 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-card-header" style="background-color: var(--gold);">
